      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-foreign-minister-willing-strengthen-communications-with-new-zealand-2024-03-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，希望在两国外长周一会晤时与新西兰加强沟通，努力维护地区和平与稳定。]]></description>
